{"tid":1674172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"清算近了，送一招不死必勝法，俾三萬警察","createTime":"2019-10-25T05:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:35:27.000Z","uid":312125,"like":101,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"332481052eae8a32f7b75af350e553014ca663da","tid":1674172,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:06:34.000Z","msg":"呢一招好簡單，就係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前網紅葵涌警署劉時沙突然砲轟林鄭，導致中央對林鄭嘅支持開始動搖，有消息傳出北京準備換人：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\">金融時報：北京將以&ldquo;臨時特首&rdquo;明春取代林鄭月娥<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20191023-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%98%8E%E6%98%A5%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%2F20191023-%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2598%25A5%25E5%258F%2596%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25A8%25A5&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=ea293081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20191023-%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%B0%87%E4%BB%A5%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E6%98%8E%E6%98%A5%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果換特首，中央會順便搞埋獨立調查委員會，到時自然會有警察落鍋，雖然唔知係邊批，但一定人心惶惶。呢個消息已經傳緊：<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>最新》<strong>郭文貴：中南海緊急會議拍板 答應香港五大訴求</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">郭文貴說，中南海會答應美國人，第一，林鄭月娥滾蛋，但律政司司長鄭若驊可能多待幾天，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後警務處長盧偉聰滾蛋</span>，保安局局長李家超待一待，過一陣子再滾蛋，<span style=\"color: red;\">然後成立由美國或者國際組織組成的獨立調查小組</span>，真普選，答應你，<span style=\"color: red;\">至於香港黑警部分，對警察進行全面調查，抓幾個起來或者免職一批警察。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E6%8B%8D%E6%9D%BF-%E7%AD%94%E6%87%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%9A%97%E5%9C%B0%E7%A7%8B%E5%BE%8C%E7%AE%97%E5%B8%B3-032352437.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25B2%25B4-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%259D%25BF-%25E7%25AD%2594%25E6%2587%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E6%259A%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%25B8%25B3-032352437.html&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTYZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a5203628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0-%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E6%8B%8D%E6%9D%BF-%E7%AD%94%E6%87%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-%E6%9A%97%E5%9C%B0%E7%A7%8B%E5%BE%8C%E7%AE%97%E5%B8%B3-032352437.html</a></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我建議嘅大招如下，請科士自行cap 圖俾同袍睇：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b7636d5eea6b501c1506521a9acb1b0b8fd05c","tid":1674172,"uid":201678,"like":44,"dislike":4,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"執法要道歉 簡直天方夜譚"},{"pid":"73f291d0801aba33697fcf466807c7d8c2d15748","tid":1674172,"uid":15205,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"快啲篤灰就差唔多"},{"pid":"d2e4b02efcf9dd0aaca87cef50225fa7cc58e041","tid":1674172,"uid":165683,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T06:54:56.000Z","msg":"